A. Minimize Cost
B. Normal (Default)
C. Maximize Reliability
D. Maximize Throughput
E. Minimize Delay; A
When the 4-bit TOS field's value is 0001, it represents the request for minimizing cost as a type of service.
What are the first six bits in the code point subfield of Differentiated services used for?
